data.name: Local-File-Organizer
data.description: An AI-powered file management tool that ensures privacy by organizing local texts, images, and PDFs. Using Google Gemma 2-2B and Llava v1.6 models with the Nexa SDK, it intuitively scans, restructures, and organizes files for quick, seamless access and easy retrieval.
